[FILE:287:descriptions/desc.primary]
This is a small library that implements epoll on top of kqueue. It has 
been successfully used to port libinput, libevdev, Wayland and more 
software to FreeBSD.

It is known to work on the following operating systems:

* DragonFly BSD
* FreeBSD
* MidnightBSD
* NetBSD
* OpenBSD
* macOS


